Summary: Observed as a possible silver diamond in shape approximately 10,000+ feet high
divs: sighting detailsi was lolling on the beach and observed a pulse jet, diamond shape aircraft\ufo traveling rapidly overhead. object went from horizon to horizon in approximately 2 or less minutes. observed through binoculars. i have spent 42 years working for the us dept of defense and never witnessed anything travel so fast. i do not think it was the sr-71 as it is not a pulse jet and they do not fly as fast as this observation. i lost sight of the object when it went over to the western horizon.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Lajes, Praia da Vitória
